    "title": "Network tray icon should open peers window, add button to disable network there",
    "body": "I doubt many users are looking for a quick way to disable the network:\r\n<img width=\"248\" alt=\"Schermafbeelding 2020-09-16 om 13 56 57\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10217/93334019-83162880-f824-11ea-9ea1-f950f3392fe3.png\">\r\n\r\nMore likely, at least from my experience, they want to see the list of peers.\r\n\r\nI suggest linking this icon to the peers tab. And then add a button there to disable the network.\r\n",
